{"tid":1246621,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"「自由」定係「豬」？反駁網上另一個嘅頻譜分析","createTime":"2019-06-20T20:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T01:18:40.000Z","uid":48729,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d838d07e1178d2a84b1c0a3ef95880b49f12c5d3","tid":1246621,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:13:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>關於之前嗰個「自由hai1」定係「豬hai1」嘅問題。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z1Foq62layA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz1Foq62layA&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=28b0fe20\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z1Foq62layA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>深夜開工嘅時候，有朋友 send 咗呢個分析俾我睇，我睇落覺得唔係好對路，所以我決定寫篇文去重新做一次分析。我本身唔係做語音學嘅，如果有嘢講錯請指正。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lanstonchu.wordpress.com/2019/06/20/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E8%B1%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanstonchu.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F06%2F20%2F%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25B1%25AC%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=bc360144\" target=\"_blank\">https://lanstonchu.wordpress.com/2019/06/20/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E8%B1%AC/</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅做法係用網上嘅單音節錄音合成，再比較合成出嚟嘅發音，同埋片段入面嘅發音，喺頻譜上有冇相似之處。而佢最後嘅答案係「豬」。我覺得呢個做法唔係太好：首先唔應該用唔同性別、年齡層嘅清晰合成錄音，去同充滿雜音嘅現場錄音比較，另外亦唔應該單憑肉眼比對頻譜去下定論。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下講講我嘅做法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先係清咗雜音先</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNPY4vL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNPY4vL.png&h=43f1ce4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>清潔後</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsDfnhu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsDfnhu.png&h=1c23306c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>合返做單聲道</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugJCACA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugJCACA.png&h=d3c10cb8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>清理完之後，可以用一個叫 Praat 嘅程式打開。清過之前好多，但係其實都仲係好嘈嘅。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.fon.hum.uva.nl/praat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fon.hum.uva.nl%2Fpraat%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=29e74cda\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fon.hum.uva.nl/praat/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n語音檔案：<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-505796604/what-hai1-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-505796604%2Fwhat-hai1-again&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=a7ce1a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-505796604/what-hai1-again</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>放咗入 Praat 之後，會出到呢個樣。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfTi4v1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfTi4v1.png&h=02304407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中下面嘅部份就係「頻譜圖」（spectrogram），而上面嘅部份係聲波圖（waveform）。頻譜其實已經有齊晒聽覺上理解語言所需要嘅資訊。因為每一個音之所以唔同，都係發音器官嘅位置同郁動、氣流嘅進出、聲帶喺唔同時候嘅震動等等聲道（vocal tract）嘅形狀改變，影響咗聲波；所以無論輔音嘅位置、發聲方法，元音嘅舌位前後高低，高低音，都應該可以揾返相應嘅物理機制，就算有其他雜訊影響，都可以用頻譜圖去揾返、估返原來嘅面貌。<br />\n<br />\n語音學上，最基礎嘅分析程序就係做 Fourier Transform，將個音波拆返做唔同嘅構成部份：即係基頻（fundamental frequency，又叫 F0）同埋唔同嘅共振峰（formant）。基頻 F0 反映嘅係音高（pitch），一般嚟講越大越高音，越細越低音。至於發咗咩元音呢，主要係睇第一共振峰（F1, first formant）同第二共振峰（F2, second formant）。微細嘅元音特徵（例如美式英文同北京話嘅捲脷）就要睇埋第三共振峰（F3, third formant）。<span style=\"color: teal;\">F1 可以反映條脷嘅高低，越低越大、越高越細；</span><span style=\"color: red;\">F2 就反映條脷嘅前後，越前越大，越後越細。</span>粵語有兩個前高元音 [ i ]（即係自嘅元音）、 [ y ]（即係豬嘅元音），佢哋嘅 F1細、F2大。（你可能會問有冇一個實數可以判斷呢？唔好意思，每個人嘅口腔大細都唔同，唔係靠絕對值去感知，我哋個腦係要識得調節嘅。）留意 [ i ] 同  [ y ] 都係單元音，係冇動程（movement）嘅，條脷應該唔使大幅移動。<br />\n<br />\n當然啲數就唔係我計，係 Praat 幫手揾出嚟。我只係好懶噉切好音節，之後佢就會俾一堆數字我。不過做呢個步驟之前其實係要切開咗音節先嘅。以下係我用我聽到嘅去切。如果我錯咗，即係前段真係單一個音節「豬」的話，頭兩截我應該會見到係同一個元音至係。另外一個難點就係「由」呢個音節嘅輔音係 [ j ]，佢嘅特性係同元音 [ i ] 嘅呈現非常相似，所以兩個音節之間嘅邊界有啲模糊。揾咗呢一堆數字，就可以進入下一個部份。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下係假設有三個音節嘅切分（segmentation）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/21/040510_dbf6cc0648ce32e797bf76125e16f01a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F21%2F040510_dbf6cc0648ce32e797bf76125e16f01a.png&h=2020885c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用呢個切法，攞咗一堆數字會得出啲咩圖表呢？其實真正嘅語音學家係會用 R 呢類神秘嘅工具，不過一嚟我唔熟、二嚟我有啲懶，所以俾我偷懶一次用 Google sheets 好唔好？下面啲圖好求其，唔係靚靚嘅 ggplot，希望大家唔好介意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第一個音節</strong><br />\n理論上係「自」嘅元音，呢一部份冇動程，基本上都係<span style=\"color: teal;\">F1（藍線）喺 500Hz 左近</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">F2 （紅線）大概喺 2000Hz 左右</span>。毫無疑問係前高元音嚟。至於係 [ i ] 定係 [ y ] 就要睇 F3，呢度唔理住。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhrQbbC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhrQbbC.png&h=0386dc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二個音節</strong><br />\n一開頭係 [ i ] 嚟嘅，跟住 <span style=\"color: teal;\">F1 變大，即係條脷放低咗</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">F2 變細，即係條脷後咗</span>。呢個移動代表<strong>佢由 [ i ] 過渡緊去一個低元音，可能係 [ ɐ ] 或者 [ a ]</strong>。<span style=\"color: red;\">中後段 F2 忽然升高</span>，似乎係由於 F1 同 F2 太接近疊住咗，所以表入面嘅 F2 嘅值，本來可能係 F3 嚟（即係測量問題﹐可以無視先）。到音節嘅終點，幅圖嘅右邊，兩條線喺低位重疊，F1 同 F2 都喺好低嘅位置，反映<span style=\"color: teal;\">舌位高（由 F1反映）</span>而<span style=\"color: red;\">後（由F2反映）</span>，即係 [ u ] 嘅位置。有咁明顯嘅動程，冇咩可能係單元音。佢係「由」嘅機會相當大。F1 同 F2 最後嘅位置有冇可能係其他音節影響呢？佢後面已經係氣聲（h），唔係受咗後面嘅元音影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEwc8Y3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEwc8Y3.png&h=c8923570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>第三個音節</strong><br />\n既然都整得，睇埋第三個音節。呢個音節拉到極長，不過唔影響個動程，你會見到佢都係由低央元音（<span style=\"color: teal;\">藍線嘅 F1 由 900 左近，上升一排之後逐漸下降</span>）慢慢過渡去前高元音（降到 800 以下，複元音一般唔會去到目標值）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1njOZb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1njOZb.png&h=0859e4af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>睇咗咁多幅圖之後我嘅結論係咩呢？聽一個音節係咩元音，最主要係睇 F1 同 F2，其次係睇 F3。唔可以就噉 zoom out 去用啲點嘅分佈去估。經過呢個簡單嘅分析，我嘅結論係由於錄音前半有明顯嘅動程，所以唔可能係「豬」呢個單元音嘅字。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>完</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>原文</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/@chaaak/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%AC%9B%E5%98%85%E4%BF%82-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E5%AE%9A%E4%BF%82-%E8%B1%AC-9d0ff31e6bc5?sk=4bd3421a500d959da4e6d526fc855216&amp;fbclid=IwAR0vpOBeZi-1SHgrcGy_cf8wry3gx9BVI8I3zl0GLjz8rcEam0kxA2Sf7lI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40chaaak%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590-%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2598%2585%25E4%25BF%2582-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1-%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BF%2582-%25E8%25B1%25AC-9d0ff31e6bc5%3Fsk%3D4bd3421a500d959da4e6d526fc855216%26fbclid%3DIwAR0vpOBeZi-1SHgrcGy_cf8wry3gx9BVI8I3zl0GLjz8rcEam0kxA2Sf7lI&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=efa14c1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@chaaak/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%AC%9B%E5%98%85%E4%BF%82-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E5%AE%9A%E4%BF%82-%E8%B1%AC-9d0ff31e6bc5?sk=4bd3421a500d959da4e6d526fc855216&amp;fbclid=IwAR0vpOBeZi-1SHgrcGy_cf8wry3gx9BVI8I3zl0GLjz8rcEam0kxA2Sf7lI</a></span>"},{"pid":"93bb3ee29e9f1ea0e9dbd32b65ad6c2d25fde486","tid":1246621,"uid":1139,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:17:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6349eb2554a2339d9cf0d20241eeb4e4c09b3371","tid":124